0e1ndor K\u00f3nya]], Hungarian opera singer\n* {{Interlanguage link multi|P\u00e1l Jakucs|hu|3=Jakucs P\u00e1l}}, Hungarian botanist, ecologist\n\n== References ==\n<references />\n* {{GEOnet|-865803}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Commons category|Sarkad}}\n* {{Official website|http://www.sarkad.hu/}} in Hungarian\n\n{{Sarkad District}}\n{{B\u00e9k\u00e9s}}\n\n[[Category:Populated places in B\u00e9k\u00e9s County]]\n\n{{Bekes-geo-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Ser Amantio di Nicolao", "label": "safe", "comment": "add authority control", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sarkad,_Hungary"}
