]]\n| utc_offset        = +1\n| utc_offset_DST    = +2\n| registration_plate = [[Vehicle registration plates of Austria|LZ]]\n| postal_code_type   = [[List of postal codes in Austria|Postal code]]\n| postal_code        = 9962\n| area_code_type = [[Telephone numbers in Austria|Area code]]\n| area_code      = 04879\n| website   = [http://kd277.www.cable24.at/stageLive/index.php?CurrentId=3&LangId=1 Homepage der Gemeinde]\n| footnotes = \n}}\n'''Sankt Veit in Defereggen''' is a municipality in the district of [[Lienz (district)|Lienz]] in the [[Austria]]n state of [[state of Tyrol|Tyrol]].\n\n==Geography==\nSankt Veit lies in the central Defereggen valley and is the municipality in Eastern Tyrol with the highest elevation. It lies on the sunny side of the valley, and in the past grain and potatoes were raised there. However, there can be snowfall even in the summer months.\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n== External links ==\n* [https://archive.is/20121230033851/http://kd277.www.cable24.at/stageLive/index.php?CurrentId=3&LangId=1 Homepage der Gemeinde] - town website\n\n{{Commons category|St. Veit in Defereggen}}\n\n{{Cities and towns in Lienz (district)}}\n\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n[[Category:Villgraten Mountains]]\n[[Category:Cities and towns in Lienz District]]\n\n\n{{Tyrol-geo-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox settlement\n| name            = St. Veit in Defereggen\n| native_name     = \n| settlement_type = \n<!-- Images     -->\n| image_skyline   = \n| imagesize       = \n| image_caption   = \n| image_shield    = wappen at st veit in defereggen.png\n| shield_size     = 80x110px\n| shield_link     = \n<!-- Maps           -->\n| pushpin_map         = Austria\n| pushpin_mapsize     = 270\n| pushpin_map_caption = Location within Austria\n| image_map           = Sankt Veit in Defereggen.png\n| mapsize             = 260x260px\n| map_alt             =\n| map_caption         = Location within Lienz district\n<!-- Location    -->\n| coordinates       = {{coord|46|55|