on. It lies on the sunny side of the valley, and in the past grain and potatoes were raised there. However, there can be snowfall even in the summer months.\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n== External links ==\n* [https://archive.is/20121230033851/http://kd277.www.cable24.at/stageLive/index.php?CurrentId=3&LangId=1 Homepage der Gemeinde] - town website\n\n{{Commonscat|St. Veit in Defereggen}}\n\n{{Cities and towns in Lienz (district)}}\n\n[[Category:Villgraten Mountains]]\n[[Category:Cities and towns in Lienz District]]\n\n\n{{Tyrol-geo-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Ser Amantio di Nicolao", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eExternal links:add authority control", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sankt_Veit_in_Defereggen"}
